parameters.name: ApprovedPatchesEnableNonSecurity
parameters.description: Specifies whether the approved patch involves updates other than security-related updates.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries returned per page.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the patch baseline.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The token that is used to retrieve the next page of results.

parameters.name: OperationSystem
parameters.description:
The type of the operating system. Valid values:

*   Windows
*   Ubuntu
*   CentOS
*   Debian
*   AliyunLinux
*   RedhatEnterpriseLinux
*   Anolis
*   AlmaLinux

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource group.

parameters.name: ShareType
parameters.description:
The share type of the template. Valid values:

*   **Public**
*   **Private**
